    <item>
      <title>🕵️‍♂️ Claude Finally Gets Web Search (Yes, Really) 🌐🤖</title>
      <link>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/claude-web-search/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/claude-web-search/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Claude just learned how to Google.&lt;/strong&gt; 🥳🔍&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Anthropic’s chatbot, &lt;strong&gt;Claude&lt;/strong&gt;, now has web search powers! 🌐✨&lt;br&gt;&#xA;✅ Paid U.S. users can try it now&lt;br&gt;&#xA;✅ Free users &amp;amp; other countries coming soon 🌍&lt;br&gt;&#xA;✅ Only works (for now) on &lt;strong&gt;Claude 3.7 Sonnet&lt;/strong&gt; 🎵🤖&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-does-it-do-&#34;&gt;What does it do? 🤔&lt;a href=&#34;#what-does-it-do-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Claude will &lt;strong&gt;auto-search the web&lt;/strong&gt; when it needs fresh info 📰&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Delivers &lt;strong&gt;answers + receipts&lt;/strong&gt; (yep, it gives you source links!) 📎&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;No more digging through tabs like a detective 🕵️‍♀️&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;but-&#34;&gt;BUT… 👀&lt;a href=&#34;#but-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Sometimes Claude &lt;em&gt;forgets&lt;/em&gt; to search 🙄&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Sometimes Claude might still &lt;strong&gt;hallucinate&lt;/strong&gt; or grab weird info 😬&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Reminder: ALL chatbots are still chaotic when it comes to accuracy 🤡&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Study says 60% of chatbot answers are 💩. Yikes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>🧱 High Schooler Builds AI vs AI Minecraft Build Battle Site 🏆</title>
      <link>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/ai-minecraft-challenge/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/ai-minecraft-challenge/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;🔥 &lt;strong&gt;Minecraft Build-Off&amp;hellip; but make it AI.&lt;/strong&gt; 🔥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;12th-grader&lt;/strong&gt; just launched &lt;strong&gt;MC-Bench&lt;/strong&gt;, a website where AI models fight it out in &lt;strong&gt;Minecraft build battles&lt;/strong&gt; 🧱⚔️.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;The prompt? Something like:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;🗣️ “Build a tropical beach hut on a sandy shore.” 🏖️🌴&lt;br&gt;&#xA;The AI? &lt;em&gt;Goes full architect mode.&lt;/em&gt; 🏗️&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;heres-how-it-works&#34;&gt;Here’s how it works:&lt;a href=&#34;#heres-how-it-works&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;AI models go head-to-head to create Minecraft builds 🧠🎮&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Humans vote on which build looks cooler 🗳️😎&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Only &lt;em&gt;after&lt;/em&gt; you vote do you find out which AI made it 🤯&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;why-minecraft&#34;&gt;Why Minecraft?&lt;a href=&#34;#why-minecraft&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Because &lt;strong&gt;EVERYONE&lt;/strong&gt; knows what a good Minecraft pineapple looks like 🍍😂.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>🎮 Xbox’s AI Copilot: Your New Gaming Buddy (or Trash Talker) 😂</title>
      <link>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/xbox-ai-copilot/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/xbox-ai-copilot/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;🚨 &lt;strong&gt;Big news from Xbox!&lt;/strong&gt; 🚨&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Just ahead of GDC, Xbox dropped a wild one — they’re testing &lt;strong&gt;“Copilot for Gaming”&lt;/strong&gt; 🕹️, a voice-activated AI sidekick that’s here to help&amp;hellip; or roast you. Yep, it’ll straight-up trash talk you if that’s your vibe. 😎🔥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;“It can trash talk you if that’s what you need,” — &lt;em&gt;Fatima Kardar, Xbox’s VP of Gaming AI&lt;/em&gt; 😏🎙️&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-does-this-copilot-actually-do-&#34;&gt;What does this Copilot actually do? 🤔&lt;a href=&#34;#what-does-this-copilot-actually-do-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Gives you &lt;strong&gt;real-time tips&lt;/strong&gt; (e.g., which Overwatch hero you should pick based on the map 🧠).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Peeks at your past choices and says, “Bruh, maybe don’t pick Junkrat again?” 💥💀&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Suggests your next best move during clutch moments 💡.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Critiques&lt;/strong&gt; your gameplay if you’re slacking (tough love 💔).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Alerts you when your squad’s online, ready to game 🎯.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;If your friends ditch you 😭, Copilot hangs around as your chill buddy.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;but-wait-theres-more-&#34;&gt;But wait, there’s more! 🎁&lt;a href=&#34;#but-wait-theres-more-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Reminds you what went down last time you played (no more “wait, where was I?” moments) 🧩.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Auto-installs games while you’re busy raiding the fridge 🍕.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Recommends new titles that match your taste 🎮💡.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;⚠️ &lt;strong&gt;No cheating though!&lt;/strong&gt; The Copilot won’t help you break the rules — just get &lt;em&gt;better&lt;/em&gt; at them 😇.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>🧊 Roblox Drops ‘Cube’: AI That Makes 3D Stuff With Just a Prompt 🎨🤖</title>
      <link>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/roblox-cube-ai/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/roblox-cube-ai/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;🚨 &lt;strong&gt;Roblox just went full sci-fi!&lt;/strong&gt; 🚨&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;They’ve launched &lt;strong&gt;“Cube”&lt;/strong&gt;, an AI tool that lets creators make 3D objects with &lt;em&gt;just a prompt&lt;/em&gt;! 🧊✨&lt;br&gt;&#xA;➡️ &amp;ldquo;Generate an orange racing car with black stripes&amp;rdquo; 🏎️🟧&lt;br&gt;&#xA;➡️ BOOM 💥 now it’s in your game 🎮.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;And the best part?&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Cube is open source!&lt;/strong&gt; 💾 So even non-Roblox folks can tinker, build plug-ins, or make Cube smarter with their own datasets 🧑‍💻⚙️.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-else-is-roblox-cooking-&#34;&gt;What else is Roblox cooking? 🍳&lt;a href=&#34;#what-else-is-roblox-cooking-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;🔥 &lt;strong&gt;Mesh generation&lt;/strong&gt; (in beta): Type a prompt, get a 3D model. Easy peasy 🟩&lt;br&gt;&#xA;🗣️ &lt;strong&gt;Text-to-Speech&lt;/strong&gt;: NPCs now have voices, no more awkward silence 🎙️&lt;br&gt;&#xA;🎤 &lt;strong&gt;Speech-to-Text&lt;/strong&gt;: Yell &amp;ldquo;MOVE FORWARD!&amp;rdquo; and your character listens 👂&lt;br&gt;&#xA;💬 &lt;strong&gt;Text Generation&lt;/strong&gt;: Make NPCs chatty or sassier than your squad 😏&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
